幣=澳幣=澳洲元<br />\n情節就係店員按照澳洲元匯率比左澳門幣佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3968a1687b2e75a91504b796a9e6a04234c119df","tid":56993,"uid":20001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>完全唔明咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門幣同港幣差不多一兌一<br />\n如果佢以為係澳門幣仲點會MOP300兌到HKD1500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實葡幣=澳門幣<br />\n<br />\n佢以為葡幣=澳幣=澳洲元<br />\n情節就係店員按照澳洲元匯率比左澳門幣佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<br />\n成篇野係店主媽媽寫<br />\n情節：<br />\n1.店主仔仔收到300蚊葡幣（澳門幣），佢以為係300蚊澳洲元<br />\n2.店主仔仔按照澳洲元匯率，比左1560港元個客（一家三口客人）<br />\n<br />\n即是店主仔仔overpaid"},{"pid":"dab9a5d0c0943f57bdfb5a16a3d417db3903a5c4","tid":56993,"uid":13602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>完全唔明咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門幣同港幣差不多一兌一<br />\n如果佢以為係澳門幣仲點會MOP300兌到HKD1500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實葡幣=澳門幣<br />\n<br />\n佢以為葡幣=澳幣=澳洲元<br />\n情節就係店員按照澳洲元匯率比左澳門幣佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<br />\n成篇野係店主媽媽寫<br />\n情節：<br />\n1.店主仔仔收到300蚊葡幣（澳門幣），佢以為係300蚊澳洲元<br />\n2.店主仔仔按照澳洲元匯率，比左1560港元個客（一家三口客人）<br />\n<br />\n即是店主仔仔overpaid</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔解釋完全唔明篇嘢講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終極199<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有係個自己個仔自己唔睇清楚就兌咗俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95894a36dc313b5988dc196ee8b6b5003df22ea","tid":56993,"uid